Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both smiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... He smiled for real for\Nthe first time when he drew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiled from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:55.55,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(783,561)}Reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in Sai's bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an assassination list\Nthat has...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,an Anbu Black Ops member's\Nown targets recorded...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called a Bingo Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,An assassination list...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these "X" marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In all likelihood,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,they're marks indicating targets\Nthat have already been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does Sai have such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...\NWhy does Sai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Art: Super Beast Scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no "X" mark on this yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it...\NSo that's what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission wasn't to be a go-between\Nfor Orochimaru and Danzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai's true classified mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,was to assassinate Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That could never be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, he said earlier that\Nhe was going to save Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And he really smiled from\Nthe bottom of his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is what I wanted\N{\i1} to show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The picture of our dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike before, he's now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What if that was all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,an act in order\Nto forestall you, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a tool for Lord Danzo.\N{\i1}I don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So no matter what you say to me,\N{\i1}it's pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of this Bingo Book...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,could indeed be capable\Nof something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This man in the book\Nnext to Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a Jonin from\Nthe Hidden Mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the man who expressed\Na hard-line stance against the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...defeated him, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't have been\Nan easy opponent to defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that he eliminated him\Nmeans that in all likelihood,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,he must have resorted\Nto every possible means.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,An act in order\Nto forestall someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,was probably all in\Na day's work for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A smile is used\Nto carry out a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You tricked me with\N{\i1}your fake smile earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's how you use\N{\i1}a fake smile, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can you grin like that\N{\i1}after getting punched?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A smile is the best way\N{\i1}to get through a tough situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if it's a fake smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surprisingly enough,\N{\i1}everyone gets fooled...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It said that in a book...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite clear by looking\Nat each of the people listed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in this Bingo Book...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai was assigned to the disposal\Nof people dangerous to the Leaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sasuke is also\None such dangerous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Danzo's goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,was to bury Orochimaru's new flesh...\Nto bury Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai attempted\Nto approach Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't betray the Leaf.\NIt was for the sake of the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what one from\Na hard-line military faction would think up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in going on\Nabout that here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nwhat Sai was ordered to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or what that Danzo guy's\Nthinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting up with Sai\Nas quickly as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and saving Sasuke\Nis what's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's indeed as Naruto says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt Sai's Chakra earlier.\NWe need to go quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Sai is after Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then I'll stop him,\N{\i1}no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You found me out, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...I've already made\Nthe first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Danzo's objective is\Nto bury you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...take you back to the Leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Although at the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here with the intention\Nof killing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's the person who acknowledged me\N{\i1}more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...thinks of Sasuke\N{\i1}like a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll do whatever it takes\N{\i1}to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll even team up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I get chopped up\N{\i1}into pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll take Sasuke back\N{\i1}from Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a special bond\N{\i1}I was finally able to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect\Nhis bond with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the one he's desperately trying to\Ndraw closer to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bond...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You interrupted my sleep\Nfor something like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sai's Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That kid wakes up in\N{\i1}a bad mood, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To think he'd break free\Nfrom my Jutsu by force...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You!\NWhat're you really after?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do you have\Nto betray us until you're satisfied...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa...su...ke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So even you were here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then is Kakashi also with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it's not Kakashi...\NI'm his substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Kakashi will now be taking you\Nback to the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Kakashi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai! I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's my replacement, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Some soft one has once again\Njoined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted to protect\Nthe bond...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,between Naruto and me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai... I thought your mission\Nwas to kill Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My classified mission was indeed\Nthe assassination of Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've had enough of orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I now want to act on\Nmy own beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Naruto will get me\Nto remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,my past emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of get the feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it's something\Nvery important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But there must be some kind\Nof reason why Naruto and Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,have pursued you so desperately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't want to sever\Ntheir bonds with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're giving it their all\Nto secure those bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't understand it\Nall that clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sasuke...\N{\i1}you{\i0} should understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I did understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I severed the bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's just what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't narrowed the gap at all\N{\i1}since back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's up with this difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because you don't have enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have different bonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:20:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonds of hatred...\Nwith my older brother.
